text: "Original Sin" is a 2001 song by Elton John. It is the third and final single from his 26th studio album Songs from the West Coast. It went to number 18 in the US Adult Contemporary chart, number 39 in the United Kingdom and number 54 in Australia. It was nominated for an Grammy Award in 2003.
